title: Barry Andrews (musician) - Wikipedia
snippet: Barry Andrews (born 12 September 1956) is an English songwriter, singer and keyboard player who is a co-founder of Shriekback and was formerly a member of XTC and the League of Gentlemen. title: Barry Andrews (politician) - Wikipedia
snippet: Barry Andrews (born 16 May 1967) is an Irish politician who serves as a Member of the European Parliament (MEP) for the Dublin constituency. He is a member of Fianna Fáil, part of Renew Europe. He previously served as Minister of State for Children from 2008 to 2011.

snippet: Barry Andrews. Actor: The Spy Who Loved Me. Barry Andrews was born in 1944 in the UK. He is an actor, known for The Spy Who Loved Me (1977), Dracula Has Risen from the Grave (1968) and The Blood on Satan's Claw (1971).
